@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_juuenq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.exp((v0 + 1.00 * v1 + 0.20)))
    tmp = wp.abs(v2)
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.cos((v2 + 0.22 * v0 + 0.19)))
    v0 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
